TITLE: Creating a Zustand Store
DESCRIPTION: Example of creating a basic Zustand store with state and actions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/pmndrs/zustand/blob/main/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import { create } from 'zustand'

const useBearStore = create((set) => ({
  bears: 0,
  increasePopulation: () => set((state) => ({ bears: state.bears + 1 })),
  removeAllBears: () => set({ bears: 0 }),
}))
```

