TITLE: Accessing Store Values with Selectors in Zustand
DESCRIPTION: Basic example of how to access values from a Zustand store using selectors. This pattern allows selecting specific parts of the store state.
SOURCE: https://github.com/pmndrs/zustand/blob/main/docs/guides/auto-generating-selectors.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
