TITLE: Creating a Factory for Counter Stores - TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Implements a factory function to manage counter stores for various tabs. This function ensures each tab has its own instance of the counter store by utilizing a Map.
SOURCE: https://github.com/pmndrs/zustand/blob/main/docs/hooks/use-store.md#2025-04-22_snippet_15

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const createCounterStoreFactory = (
  counterStores: Map<string, ReturnType<typeof createCounterStore>>, 
) => {
  return (counterStoreKey: string) => {
    if (!counterStores.has(counterStoreKey)) {
      counterStores.set(counterStoreKey, createCounterStore())
    }
    return counterStores.get(counterStoreKey)!
  }
}
```

