TITLE: Updating Zustand Store to Track Game History
DESCRIPTION: Enhances the Zustand store to track game history by adding a history state that contains arrays of squares for each move. Implements a setHistory function to update the history state.
SOURCE: https://github.com/pmndrs/zustand/blob/main/docs/guides/tutorial-tic-tac-toe.md#2025-04-22_snippet_16

