TITLE: Creating Custom JSON Storage in Zustand
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to create a custom JSON storage implementation with serialization options for dates using createJSONStorage helper
SOURCE: https://github.com/pmndrs/zustand/blob/main/docs/integrations/persisting-store-data.md#2025-04-22_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { createJSONStorage } from 'zustand/middleware'

const storage = createJSONStorage(() => sessionStorage, {
  reviver: (key, value) => {
    if (value && value.type === 'date') {
      return new Date(value)
    }
    return value
  },
  replacer: (key, value) => {
    if (value instanceof Date) {
      return { type: 'date', value: value.toISOString() }
    }
    return value
  },
})
```

