TITLE: Implementing Time Travel in React Tic-Tac-Toe Game
DESCRIPTION: React component code that implements the time travel feature for a Tic-Tac-Toe game. It maps over the game history to create a list of buttons that allow players to jump to previous game states, with each button showing the corresponding move number.
