TITLE: Initializing LocalStorage with Position Data
DESCRIPTION: Sets up initial localStorage state with a partial position object, simulating a scenario with missing fields
SOURCE: https://github.com/pmndrs/zustand/blob/main/docs/middlewares/persist.md#2025-04-22_snippet_19

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
if (!localStorage.getItem('position-storage')) {
  localStorage.setItem(
    'position-storage',
    JSON.stringify({
      state: { position: { y: 100 } }, // missing `x` field
      version: 0,
    }),
  )
}
```

